{"tid":2171712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾鎮濤飛抵上海後興奮到即除口罩：給你們看看回到祖國的笑容！","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T13:59:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":76,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"860a4e5412887d85c178a92a453ff21c0e797691","tid":2171712,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"藝人鍾鎮濤（阿B）近年轉戰大陸密密賺人仔，近日他無懼疫情飛抵上海工作，他更拍片上載至微博記錄搭飛機的過程，只見阿B途中已經勁興奮，笑容滿面。<br />\n<br />\n影片中見到阿B全副武裝，戴齊眼罩、口罩、保護面罩，以及手套到機場。他未出發先興奮：「隔離兩個禮拜以後，到處都可以去了，到時候見。」上機之後氣氛一變，突然勁凝重地展示身上各樣防疫用具，又謂：「做好保護措施，保護自己，也保護他人。」豈料他飛抵上海機場後就興奮得立即除下口罩，高呼「給你們看看回到祖國的笑容」，口罩又戴又除，頗為冒險。"},{"pid":"53c7b68de9e6d0a5af9025031674b381532708ae","tid":2171712,"uid":16659,"like":47,"dislike":182,"score":-135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200824/374378288530984960.jpeg/SxyDYoWAaH0kO4zsLnyW9_DSBnEGhFYtYluIEWJbiBE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200824%2F374378288530984960.jpeg%2FSxyDYoWAaH0kO4zsLnyW9_DSBnEGhFYtYluIEWJbiBE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=807236b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200824/374378821396336641.jpeg/5CjVCOkX_lnIDXJqNuAa1UcSnaE6liMtnDZpeZw2aXk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200824%2F374378821396336641.jpeg%2F5CjVCOkX_lnIDXJqNuAa1UcSnaE6liMtnDZpeZw2aXk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b8336151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200824/374378823447351296.jpeg/7n2bZkWeJUV_RTprRJ9TU3cT5Tk0BVK-2ElG8NhJRvA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200824%2F374378823447351296.jpeg%2F7n2bZkWeJUV_RTprRJ9TU3cT5Tk0BVK-2ElG8NhJRvA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8ae12365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200824/374378825582252032.jpeg/